    schema:description """The goal of this subject is to deal with sustainable issues related to water. That will include the water cycle, water uses, water pollution and water treatment to improve its quality.
Furthermore, the course will include sustainable water management in industry, including the analysis of different processes considering water sustainability through case studies."""@es ;
